is square is the heart and soul of Montepulciano and the center of the town. You&#x2019;ll find some of the most important buildings here, like the Duomo (cathedral). This building might not be that impressive from the outside, but inside you&#x2019;ll find some of the town&#x2019;s most important artworks. You&#x2019;ll also find incredible frescoes, tiles, and stained glass.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2.jpg\" alt=\"Montepulciano italy things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"235\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Montepulciano italy things to do\" class=\"wp-image-82782 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1336px) 100vw, 1336px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2.jpg 1336w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-418x600.jpg 418w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-564x810.jpg 564w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-235x338.jpg 235w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-113x163.jpg 113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-125x180.jpg 125w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-534x768.jpg 534w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-713x1024.jpg 713w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-752x1080.jpg 752w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-1002x1440.jpg 1002w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-300x431.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-600x862.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-150x216.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133109\/Montepulciano-italy-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In Piazza Grande, you&#x2019;ll also see the Palazzo Comunale, which is a beautiful clock tower. Best of all, you can climb to the top for amazing views!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>After you&#x2019;ve visited the main buildings, sit in the square for a while and take in the hustle and bustle of Montepulciano.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-montepulciano\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Montepulciano.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6.jpg\" alt=\"Piazza Grande Montepulciano\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Piazza Grande Montepulciano\" class=\"wp-image-82794 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21143024\/Montepulciano-italy-6-300x450.jpg 300w, ht