ads\/2021\/11\/16103906\/pienza-italy-5-600x751.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16103906\/pienza-italy-5-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16103906\/pienza-italy-5.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-visit-a-viewpoint-in-montepulciano-italy\">Visit a Viewpoint in Montepulciano, Italy<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Because of its high position, one of the top things to do in Montepulciano is to visit a viewpoint. Veduta Panoramica is a beautiful viewpoint at the edge of the historic center walls. It&#x2019;s the perfect place to come for incredible views over the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/tuscany\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tuscan<\/a> countryside, especially at sunset. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11.jpg\" alt=\"hills tucany\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"hills tucany\" class=\"wp-image-82804 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1480px) 100vw, 1480px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11.jpg 1480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-463x600.jpg 463w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-624x810.jpg 624w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-592x768.jpg 592w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-789x1024.jpg 789w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-833x1080.jpg 833w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-1110x1440.jpg 1110w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-300x389.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-600x778.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-150x195.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144058\/Montepulciano-italy-11.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The Medici Fortress is also another great option, a place of historic ruins with a great terrace viewpoint. You can also do some wine tasting here!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, the best viewpoint is at the top of Palazzo Comunale. It&#x2019;s the highest place to go for views in Montepulciano, and on a clear day, you can see <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/umbria-italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Lago di Trasimeno in Umbria<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/things-to-do-siena\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Siena<\/a> in the distance.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-montepulciano\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Montepulciano.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/82427&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21151414\/montepulciano-things-to-do-2.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21151414\/montepulciano-things-to-do-2-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21151414\/montepulciano-things-to-do-2-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Best Things to do in Montepulciano, Italy\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-sanctuary-madonna-di-san-biagio\">Sanctuary Madonna di San Biagio<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are many churches in Montepulciano (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Italy<\/a>), but one of the most beautiful and popular is the Madonna di San Biagio. This renaissance pilgrimage church was built between 1518 and 1540, so there is plenty of history to be found. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10.jpg\" alt=\"view montepulciano\"><\/noscript><img width=\"234\" height=\"338\" alt=\"view montepulciano\" class=\"wp-image-82802 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1329px) 100vw, 1329px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10.jpg 1329w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-415x600.jpg 415w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-561x810.jpg 561w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-234x338.jpg 234w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-113x163.jpg 113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-125x180.jpg 125w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-532x768.jpg 532w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-709x1024.jpg 709w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-748x1080.jpg 748w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-997x1440.jpg 997w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-300x433.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-600x867.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-150x217.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144045\/Montepulciano-italy-10.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>It&#x2019;s well known that the architect was influenced by the work of St Peter&#x2019;s Cathedral in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/rome\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Rome<\/a>, which inspired the large domed roof. Once inside, things get even more interesting with the geometric shapes and a floor plan in the shape of a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/greece\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Greek<\/a> cross. It&#x2019;s also home to the best renaissance art in the area!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Sanctuary Madonna di San Biagio is a little harder to get to than other churches in Montepulciano. It&#x2019;s outside the walls at the bottom of the hill, so it is possible to walk down to the church. However, prepare yourself for a challenging and hot walk back up afterward. Some people choose to park here before going into Montepulciano.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21133057\/Montepulciano-italy-4.jpg\" alt=\"things to do Montepulciano italy tuscany\"><\/noscript><img width=\"240\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do Montepulciano italy tuscany\" class=\"wp-image-82