o glass. Plus, it&#x2019;s a great way to learn a bit about Montepulciano&#x2019;s history. Afterward, make sure to buy some wine from the tasting or from one of the many wine shops in town.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tour \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tour\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/wine-tour-montepulciano\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your wine cellar tour in Montepulciano<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144939\/Montepulciano-italy-12.jpg\" alt=\"winery Montepulciano\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"winery Montepulciano\" class=\"wp-image-82806 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144939\/Montepulciano-italy-12.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144939\/Montepulciano-italy-12-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144939\/Montepulciano-italy-12-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144939\/Montepulciano-italy-12-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144939\/Montepulciano-italy-12-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/21144939\/Montepulciano-italy-12-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-c