t a 20-minute drive away, among the famous landscapes of Val d&#x2019;Orcia. Above all, it&#x2019;s renowned for its renaissance architecture and pecorino cheese! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-69222 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/16114605\/pienza-italy-14-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/stat